- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper draws inspiration from techniques used in robot motion planning. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper presents an efficient sampling-based framework for solving the problem. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with optimization problems and probabilistic frameworks. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the paper provides experimental results on several types of problems, which may involve image processing or computer vision techniques.
